                <a class="bg-[#25D366] text-white font-headline-md text-headline-md px-8 py-5 font-bold uppercase inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:brightness-110 transition-all" href="https://wa.me/51999999999?text=Hola%20Larminer%2C%20quiero%20informacion%20sobre%20el%20programa%20de%206%20maquinas">
